snippet.title: Intellivision Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the original Evercade handheld. All of the games here are made for the Intellivision.

Games in this cart:
00:07 - Astrosmash
03:21 - Buzz Bombers
09:33 - Frog Bog
11:43 - Night Stalker
13:52 - Pinball
15:19 - Princess Quest*
21:02 - Shark! Shark!
22:50 - Slap Shot Super Pro Hockey
27:27 - SNAFU
30:32 - Thin Ice
33:45 - Thunder Castle
38:56 - Word Rockets**

*Homebrew game
**Originally part of Learning Fun II
